data.description:
The Perfect Home: Affordable with Meticulous Upgrades

Elegantly renovated, this Southside gem offers a tastefully updated brick and concrete block home in a prime location. Boasting four bedrooms and three bathrooms, this spacious residence showcases a wealth of exquisite features. Notably, there is a second master suite, ideal for use as a mother-in-law suite, alongside a living room, family room, and an interior laundry room, all complemented by a one-car garage. This home has undergone significant upgrades, with repiping (2021), a brand-new electrical panel (2021), water heater (2021), and AC system installed (2021). The custom kitchen is a standout feature, featuring pristine white shaker cabinets, granite countertops, a stylish subway tile backsplash, and newer stainless steel appliances (2021).

High-end luxury vinyl plank flooring graces the living areas. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated, and the interior and exterior are freshly painted.

This charming property boasts a fantastic feature that's perfect for both families and pet owners - a spacious fenced-in backyard. Imagine the peace of mind knowing that your children and furry friends can play freely and safely in this private outdoor oasis.

Discover the vibrant lifestyle of Southside Jacksonville! Nestled in the heart of this thriving community, this home offers the perfect blend of modern convenience and suburban charm.
Southside is renowned for its dynamic atmosphere, boasting an array of dining, shopping, and entertainment options just moments away. Explore the trendy boutiques and restaurants at St. Johns Town Center, catch a movie at the nearby theaters, or savor the diverse culinary delights that line the streets.
